{"tid":690551,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 放珍藏個harddisk壞左","createTime":"2018-06-05T03:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T15:40:00.000Z","uid":47878,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"96c515fa62f216441308da6296000b05739209d1","tid":690551,"uid":47878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"本身有個WD 既harddisk專門放珍藏<br />\n本身1TB,依家用左800GB,用左一年<br />\n但呢兩日一開就搞到部電腦好lag<br />\nD片播播下又會死機,抆左個harddisk就會正常番<br />\n<br />\n求教點樣可以CHECK到個Harddisk係咪中左毒,定只係太多野"},{"pid":"3b36ec93eee74710d3e9d4bbe5cd51663f7dc708","tid":690551,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"試下問電腦技術員史先生"},{"pid":"47ded5a18ee67a5340d222d95b1bbacc95343e94","tid":690551,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ccleaner.com/defraggler\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccleaner.com%2Fdefraggler&d=AZAWpLf1Nx5nkV5bLvirGv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=37ef25ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ccleaner.com/defraggler</a>"},{"pid":"6c76c0a8147198c39d2189aaaca25f4da79cf102","tid":690551,"uid":35393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T17:57:55.000Z","msg":"crystal disk info<br />\n<br />\n不過九成你HDD壞左，快D做 back up"},{"pid":"d3fd1a2787de988a119ddea2c4bd061a6693e1bb","tid":690551,"uid":7977,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"叫得珍藏竟然唔做backup, 姐係唔係幾重要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf68cefbb76b5d0cb4d13ed79b05b123b7f9583","tid":690551,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9fd0aea4038bdbd586a3715384fd4938cf474ae","tid":690551,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲用開cd珍藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n壽命得5年？"},{"pid":"fcefd59baf6787efef1ca8b791f01168bd34ae06","tid":690551,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:07:32.000Z","msg":"唔好用CD、DVD做&ldquo;backup&rdquo;。另外keep得果一個copy唔叫做backup."},{"pid":"4dc1c4f7f27588bd5cd8e04bc7d205107d47a44f","tid":690551,"uid":148497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"我幾年前開始用BD同DVD M-DISC保存重要資料，好多人測試過隻碟係惡劣環境下都用到，可以保最少100年，其實唔需要100年，保到我死前就得。但香港好小見M-DISC買，我係日本買。<br />\n<br />\n部分測試去睇睇:<a href=\"http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk/mag/indexmag.html?http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk/mag/artsep16/mol-mdisc-review.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.microscopy-uk.org.uk%2Fmag%2Findexmag.html%3Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.microscopy-uk.org.uk%2Fmag%2Fartsep16%2Fmol-mdisc-review.html&d=AZAWpLf1Nx5nkV5bLvirGv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b5fa48ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk/mag/indexmag.html?http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk/mag/artsep16/mol-mdisc-review.html</a>"},{"pid":"b2623164bc28490ccd31ae1810c75ae9c5e0c514","tid":690551,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47ded5a18ee67a5340d222d95b1bbacc95343e94","tid":690551,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ccleaner.com/defraggler\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccleaner.com%2Fdefraggler&d=AZAWpLf1Nx5nkV5bLvirGv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=37ef25ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ccleaner.com/defraggler</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"唔識就唔好講，會攪死佢既珍藏。frag frag 吓停咪大獲。<br />\n我有hd同op 一樣，唔理佢冇事，有時睇緊片會死咗。翻插又冇事；我copy file 去第二個hd再做back up；神奇係個hd兩、三年重未死，一路係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eeca0b391b14ca63dd905cb50d